Detailed Description

The C++ wrapper for the nitf_Field.

The Field is a generic type object that allows storage and casting of data amongst disparate data types.

std::string nitf::Object< nitf_Field , MemoryDestructor<nitf_Field > >::getObjectID (  )  const [inline, inherited]

Returns an ID that represents this particular object. Currently, the ID is the stringized memory address of the underlying memory.

This *could* be used for equality purposes, however be warned, because as objects die, etc. the memory addresses will be reused.
